description:
In continuation of the State of Qatar’s efforts to combat the global outbreak of the Coronavirus (COVID-19) and halt its spread among citizens and residents, His Excellency the Prime Minister and Minister of Interior has decided (as of March 20) to take precautionary measures and ban all forms of gatherings by law, including but not limited to the Corniche, public parks, beaches and social gatherings.

Measures include the following:

Deploying mobile patrols and detaining anyone who violates this decision;
Establishing check points across the country;
Dedicating a hotline: 44579999 – to receive reports and complaints related to any violations of this law and previous laws.
